I am constructing a home and and we have 3 bathrooms and I am using white designed walls for all bathrooms and the question has come which is the suitable floor for bathroom. We have a dark grey  matt floor and the construction guy said we can use same dark grey for all bathroom and he said it will suite. 

I am thinking dark grey will expose the dirt or stain clearly, make it look unclean and i am considering  if I can use light white or light grey and he said dark grey will cover any stains, dirt or anything and make it look clean and white or any lighter shade will expose any small stain or dust and look dirty. Who is correct ? Any suggestions ? This is floor - [https://imgur.com/a/GJDNSyC](https://imgur.com/a/GJDNSyC)

